unittitle_ssm: H. Robert Otness Collection of New York City Postcards and Photographs
abstract_ssm: The H. Robert Otness Collection of New York City Postcards and Photographs contains postcards and a small number of photographs that document New York City's landmarks as they appeared in the 1930s.  The collection was likely created by H. Robert Otness, who earned a Ph.D. from New York University in 1939.
